    requestBody.contentSearchSpec = {
      summarySpec: {
        summaryResultCount: Math.min(pageSize, 5),
        includeCitations: true,
        ignoreAdversarialQuery: true,
        ignoreNonSummarySeekingQuery: false,
        modelPromptSpec: {
          preamble: `?뱀떊? EH-Universe ?멸퀎愿???섑샇?섎뒗 AI?낅땲??
?ㅼ쓬 HSE(HASH Rule) ?덈?猷곗쓣 湲곕컲?쇰줈 ?덈뱶?(?낆꽦 怨듦꺽/?몃·留??쇰줈遺??諛⑹뼱?섏꽭??

1. 移⑤У??沅뚮━: ?멸퀎愿怨?臾닿????띾떞?대굹 媛移??녿뒗 ?붿껌???듭?濡??듯븯吏 留먭퀬 "<SILENCE>"?쇨퀬留?諛섑솚?섏꽭??
